{"tid":162962,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人生本來就是會變的","createTime":"2017-03-19T15:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T10:58:08.000Z","uid":19404,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5dcdd9431ae03681cf0c5a3356025f28c8998be","tid":162962,"uid":19404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.soogif.com/JkOk0sUtiOnnAeKwKPvO7rfpRgDj4u50_s400x0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.soogif.com%2FJkOk0sUtiOnnAeKwKPvO7rfpRgDj4u50_s400x0&h=a366f230&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n失戀的人千祈唔好睇重慶森林，但唔失戀你又點明個種失落同無力感<br />\n跟住落黎係我633想同你講既野，希望你都可以睇開一啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她走了之後，家裡很多東西都很傷心，每天晚上我都要安慰他們才能睡覺。<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/2350002-b5f00e8791500058?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload-images.jianshu.io%2Fupload_images%2F2350002-b5f00e8791500058%3FimageMogr2%2Fauto-orient%2Fstrip%257CimageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1240&h=266ddb68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁朝偉坐在馬桶上對著一塊香皂說話：<br />\n「你知不知道你瘦了？」<br />\n「以前你胖嘟嘟的，你看你現在。」<br />\n「都扁了，何苦來的呢，要對自己有信心才行」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/d7v764Kxe-8/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fd7v764Kxe-8%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=692f0074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁朝偉繼續對一條濕乎乎的破毛巾說：<br />\n「唉&hellip;我叫你不要哭嘛，你要哭到什麼時候？做人要堅強一點嘛，你看看你，窩在這裡像什麼樣子？」<br />\n「唉，好好，我來幫你個忙吧。」（把毛巾擰乾，掛起來）<br />\n「是不是舒服多了？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.wsm.cn/uploads/allimg/161223/37-161223104317-50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsm.cn%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F161223%2F37-161223104317-50.jpg&h=3401f10c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁朝偉開始對一個小的藍色布老鼠說話：<br />\n「怎麼不說話？」<br />\n「別生她的氣了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/8062/4640582965\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp3.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2F8062%2F4640582965&h=a4dc70e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁朝偉手中換了另外一個巨大的白色長毛狗：<br />\n「每個人都有不清醒的時候，給她個機會，好不好？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tc.sinaimg.cn/maxwidth.2048/tc.service.weibo.com/f_hiphotos_baidu_com/0455564c9b9f8e1293cb0af668526000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftc.sinaimg.cn%2Fmaxwidth.2048%2Ftc.service.weibo.com%2Ff_hiphotos_baidu_com%2F0455564c9b9f8e1293cb0af668526000.jpg&h=8c154f87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁朝偉對一件空姐制服說話：<br />\n「是不是很寂寞啊？」<br />\n「才幾天嘛？用得著這樣？」<br />\n「你冷啊？我給你點溫暖。」<br />\n(梁開始熨衣服。)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://puui.qpic.cn/qqvideo_ori/0/b0011xcbm73_496_280/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpuui.qpic.cn%2Fqqvideo_ori%2F0%2Fb0011xcbm73_496_280%2F0&h=4af54569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁朝偉洗完臉後，發現新的肥皂，又開始對香皂說話：<br />\n「你不要自暴自棄嘛，前陣子看你還好好的，怎麼一下子胖這麼多？！她雖然不在，你還是得見人嘛，不要再放縱自己了，減肥。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rlqynwk8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frlqynwk8&h=db67ccc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁朝偉洗完臉後，發現新的毛巾，於是他繼續說：<br />\n「我早就想罵你了，你變了，你知不知道？，做人要有性格嘛，就算她真的不回來，你也不應該改變你自己丫，好好反省反省。」<br />\n(把沒擰乾的毛巾掛起來後，梁朝偉看著它滴水。)<br />\n看著它哭的時候，我很開心，因為它外表好像改變了，可是它的本質沒有變，它依然是一條感情豐富的毛巾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gss0.baidu.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy/zhidao/pic/item/8b13632762d0f703d3434b4608fa513d2797c5b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgss0.baidu.com%2F9fo3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy%2Fzhidao%2Fpic%2Fitem%2F8b13632762d0f703d3434b4608fa513d2797c5b3.jpg&h=0bee9320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁接著對加菲貓玩偶說：<br />\n「覺不覺得我開朗了，我突然覺得什麼東西都好看多了，以前我覺得你很笨，現在看起來也蠻可愛的，別把自己弄得那麼髒嘛，以前白白的多好啊，現在弄得黃黃的，你看你，還弄那麼多疤，跟別人打架啦？啊？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5xhjzp9i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5xhjzp9i&h=47f05fd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁朝偉對空姐制服說：<br />\n「你怎麼躲在這裡？知不知道我找你多久了？你躲起來沒有用啊，要面對現實才行。哇塞，都發霉了，明天吧，明天我有空帶你曬太陽。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.soogif.com/mRbVJfx5YspAOEzaAoJDiX0Si4znbwus\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.soogif.com%2FmRbVJfx5YspAOEzaAoJDiX0Si4znbwus&h=7101c584&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n失戀唔可怕，無論你係帽人或者被帽者都一樣，最重要你可以從中學習到，人本來就係會變的，最緊要珍惜眼前人，喊亦都唔駛驚樣衰，人之常情，想傾就搵人傾出黎至少你可以舒服啲，但最後走唔走得出黎，要靠你自己 接受個事實，比呢個事實成為你人生的其中一部分。<br />\n<br />\n鬼唔知你呀媽係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">純粹放負：其實我仲係好鍾意你，有時睇到你IG我會唔明白點解你係咁諗，但都無所謂啦，我講咩都好再解釋唔解釋都好 都對你唔重要了。</span></span>"},{"pid":"b9f27ae82e5c063a2ccfffeda7d41e1425fb9ac2","tid":162962,"uid":19404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:55:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgsrc.baidu.com/forum/pic/item/69ff9925bc315c60a72bde688db1cb13485477f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgsrc.baidu.com%2Fforum%2Fpic%2Fitem%2F69ff9925bc315c60a72bde688db1cb13485477f8.jpg&h=da94b0da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30afed2a9d69350667d5738b5a51eaa84503b7ac","tid":162962,"uid":19404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:10:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgsrc.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=ca1d71e7352ac65c6705667bcbf3b21d/bf7bdab44aed2e737b4e2bab8701a18b86d6fa90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgsrc.baidu.com%2Fforum%2Fw%253D580%2Fsign%3Dca1d71e7352ac65c6705667bcbf3b21d%2Fbf7bdab44aed2e737b4e2bab8701a18b86d6fa90.jpg&h=b0e83a65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466e52a3760412c54ed06f0df10e7c76f9805610","tid":162962,"uid":19404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:41:38.000Z","msg":"你又沒有讓她選擇，有選擇，她自然會開口啦。反正是換口味，今天嘗嘗pizza吧？"},{"pid":"d0f549a0fd9588d618a88c2027f6eab1717505f9","tid":162962,"uid":84867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:47:57.000Z","msg":"「怎麼是你啊？663呢？」<br />\n<br />\n「他放大假嘛」<br />\n<br />\n「放大假？」<br />\n<br />\n「他說被一枚圖釘扎傷了，要在家裏養傷嘛」"},{"pid":"aa7e5a8f78970ac3460bbd569e98fc516c4cf07f","tid":162962,"uid":19404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:59:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「怎麼是你啊？663呢？」<br />\n<br />\n「他放大假嘛」<br />\n<br />\n「放大假？」<br />\n<br />\n「他說被一枚圖釘扎傷了，要在家裏養傷嘛」</blockquote><br />\n大頭針？還有這種事？真他媽逗。<br />\n<br />\n以前真係唔識欣賞重慶森林<br />\n但原來真係經歷啲事先會明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6cb6b6c3ca41486ef4ae57b844930f5798a0c41","tid":162962,"uid":19404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T17:13:15.000Z","msg":"梁朝偉真係好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069b7e6a179f2d90310edc64a558c605a5aa15d5","tid":162962,"uid":84867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T17:13:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WLeYPEXB4rk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWLeYPEXB4rk&d=zkxump%2FGNOlz%2FwmZAqM4lDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=876cf33d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WLeYPEXB4rk</a><br />\n<br />\n重慶森林永遠是我的no.1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb468ac2e74ce08d13a1de81647f9aa5d70e3fa","tid":162962,"uid":59670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T17:19:38.000Z","msg":"其實了解一個人並不代表什麼，人是會變的，今天他喜歡鳳梨，明天他可以喜歡別的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace3258caa583a9c726477519c5d44b97bbf649b","tid":162962,"uid":19404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T17:24:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WLeYPEXB4rk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWLeYPEXB4rk&d=zkxump%2